descriptionHtml:
A new dungeon fairly small and east of Riverwood. It does require a certain amount of skill to get whats inside. I would suggest being level 30 or higher. It has 2 leveled chests and a pretty powerful sword. But also has 4 Dwarven spheres guarding it.. IMPORTANT don\'t use as player home will lose stuff put in chests! If there any bugs notify me and i will fix them. and if you enjoyed it endorse me. Sorry about no pictures they take to long to upload to skyrim nexus.

Also thing its kind of dark in some parts of the dungeon tommorow ill make one with more lighting for the people who want it. One more thing if you would like to use my mod go ahead and use it for any purpose just credit me where i should be credited.
author: Zeno
